lead_paragraph: Jeff Bagwell and Tim Raines might want to block off the date for the 2017 induction ceremony at the baseball Hall of Fame after falling just short of election this year.

headline.print_headline: Bagwell, Raines and Hoffman Fall Just Short of Hall Election
